AWKA – Ahead of the 2023 general elections, the spiritual leader of the Igbo nation, Chief Rommy Ezeonwuka (Ogilisi Igbo), has offered to render spiritual help with the substance of Ogilisi powers to politicians aspiring for various political positions with a view to aid them to success both at the party primary elections and the main elections. Positions up for grabs in the 2023 poll included the president, state governorship seats, Senate, Federal House of Representatives and State Houses of Assembly seats. Addressing journalists in Oba Idemili-South local government area of Anambra State, Ezeonwuka described the Ogilisi as a phenomenal natural substance discovered by the ancestors for several purposes such as cleansing, protection and to accelerate pace for people to succeed and make progress in their chosen endeavours, adding that the power of Ogilisi could work anywhere in the world, not only in Igboland. He said: “Ogilisi is a tested and trusted natural substance for dealing with human errors, protection of people against injustice, against oppression, against disastrous tendencies and to prevent failure and disappointment.”